                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270531-185-off980 t18270531-185-cd981"></join>, 1 curtain, value 6d.; 1 handkerchief, value 1s.; 5 knives, value 1s.; 6 forks, value 1s.; 2 wine glasses, value 2s.; 1 cup and saueer, value 2d.; 2 towels, value 2d.; 2 caps, value 1s.; 1 frock, value 2s., and 1 frock-body, value 1s.
